{"tid":2043412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣6月6罷免韓國瑜 香港人可以幫手!","createTime":"2020-05-30T11:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T14:49:33.000Z","uid":240968,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"786bb424695057be4ef7d45e7fa33c1452aea896","tid":2043412,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"(略長文，總結在最底)<br />\n<br />\n根據台灣公職人員選舉罷免法第53條:<br />\n<br />\n政黨及任何人於投票日<span style=\"color: red;\">前十日</span>起至投票時間截止前，不得以任何方式，發布有關候選人、被罷免人或選舉、罷免之民意調查資料，亦不得加以報導<br />\n、散布、評論或引述。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">台灣人現在不能發放跟評論民調，但無禁止身處香港的香港人評論</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第56條(二) 更指明:<br />\n於<span style=\"color: red;\">投票日從事競選、助選或罷免活動</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">投票當日，台灣人都不能拉票，但無禁止身處香港的香港人拉票</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你支持台灣民主，或者支持攬炒，韓國瑜絕對需要被罷免! 但市民出門意欲唔高，可能罷免失敗，所以香港朋友可以幫手繼續宣傳! <span style=\"color: gold;\">韓國瑜輸，國共兩黨就會一齊輸</span>!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4600475e1099ec525a8f24ee45770bde186b8985","tid":2043412,"uid":240968,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:46:02.000Z","msg":"新聞都俾埋大家: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.ltn.com.tw/m/article/ALK_pfSX1Tg/PLI7xntdRxhw36MghLam-OL4CYu7clSZkF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2FALK_pfSX1Tg%2FPLI7xntdRxhw36MghLam-OL4CYu7clSZkF&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypDwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=4cb422f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2FALK_pfSX1Tg%2FPLI7xntdRxhw36MghLam-OL4CYu7clSZkF&h=c70fa221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://video.ltn.com.tw/m/article/ALK_pfSX1Tg/PLI7xntdRxhw36MghLam-OL4CYu7clSZkF</a>"},{"pid":"694945753727457b90632c1b2f81f8dcfc7b5258","tid":2043412,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"